  "title": "Production Management Trainee",
  "description": "<p>We are from central kitchen in food manufacturing sector located in Singapore, fostering a positive work environment—\"Work Hard, Play Hard!\" We're looking for passionate management professionals to join our family!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Position:</strong> Production Management Trainee</p>\n<p><strong>Monthly Salary:</strong> From $3,000 onwards</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Learn and understand all aspects of food production, quality control, and safety standards.</li>\n  <li>Assist in production planning and execution to meet daily targets.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with production supervisors to manage workflow and manpower allocation.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and report on production efficiency, waste reduction, and process improvements.</li>\n  <li>Ensure adherence to food safety, hygiene, and regulatory requirements.</li>\n  <li>Participate in hands-on training across various production functions.</li>\n  <li>Assist in equipment maintenance coordination and troubleshooting minor issues.</li>\n  <li>Support process optimization projects and suggest improvements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong leadership and problem-solving skills.</li>\n  <li>Willingness to learn and work in a fast-paced production environment.</li>\n  <li>Strong problem-solving and analytical skills.</li>\n  <li>Good communication and teamwork abilities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p>✔ 20 days of paid leave</p>\n<p>✔ Medical benefits &amp; insurance coverage</p>\n<p>✔ Various allowances &amp; incentives (Meal allowances, Revenue Incentives, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Various bonuses (AWS, performance, attendance)</p>\n<p>✔ Various rewards (Best Employee Award, Long services award, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Strong career progression opportunities</p>\n<p>✔ Revenue incentives</p>\n<p>✔ Sponsored courses for career growth</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>If you’re the right fit for our team, send your application here! We look forward to your application!</strong></p>",
